text: 43 Squadron or 43rd Squadron may refer to: * No. 43 Squadron RAAF, a unit of the Royal Australian Air Force * No. 43 Squadron RAF, a unit of the United Kingdom Royal Air Force * 43d Fighter Squadron, a unit of the United States Air Force * 43d Flying Training Squadron, a unit of the United States Air Force * 43d Aeromedical Evacuation Squadron, a unit of the United States Air Force ==See also== * 43rd Division (disambiguation) * 43rd Group (disambiguation) * 43rd Brigade (disambiguation) * 43rd Regiment (disambiguation) * 43rd Battalion (disambiguation)
title: 43 Squadron
